<body>
Reports an object property that can be converted to ES6 shorthand style and provides a quick-fix to do it.
<!-- tooltip end -->
<p>Example:</p>
<pre><code>
var obj = {foo:foo}
</code></pre>
<p>After applying the quick-fix the code looks as follows:</p>
<pre><code>
var obj = {foo}
</code></pre>

</body>
</html>